{"id": "1498221333970944000", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 0, "author_id": "265494179222650891", "author_name": "haps", "author_bot": false, "content": "Why everything under only 1 column <a:dies:1155235812515008694>", "timestamp": "2026-04-27T07:16:41.625000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1498221333513900042", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 9540, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1402941858606219294/1498221333513900042/image.png?ex=6a3249d9&is=6a30f859&hm=a91a3cdfc5cb695d46cf6357cd140c3d1e8a4abc9b6d500ad8a8387f38029d5d&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1498221805775753226", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 19, "author_id": "183782216353054720", "author_name": "omnichromia", "author_bot": false, "content": "Hiya! Your regional delimiting character is not set correctly to `,`. We've run into this issue before. Gimme a sec to pull up what you need to do rq", "timestamp": "2026-04-27T07:18:34.112000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["265494179222650891"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1498221333970944000", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1498223318862401548", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 19, "author_id": "183782216353054720", "author_name": "omnichromia", "author_bot": false, "content": "The exact instructions differ slightly between versions of Windows, but assuming that you're using Windows:\nGo to Settings —> Time & Language —> Language & Region —> Number Format (may be under \"Regional Format\") and confirm that your settings are as follows:\n- Decimal symbol: `.`\n- Digit grouping symbol: `,`\n- List separator: `,`", "timestamp": "2026-04-27T07:24:34.860000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["265494179222650891"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1498221333970944000", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1498223742105554965", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 0, "author_id": "183782216353054720", "author_name": "omnichromia", "author_bot": false, "content": "If you give me a day or two, I'll also have the new source files compiled into an .xlsx in my repo (and I'll upload it here too) but right now I need to sleeps", "timestamp": "2026-04-27T07:26:15.769000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1498223962533138602", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 19, "author_id": "265494179222650891", "author_name": "haps", "author_bot": false, "content": "I changed that, but it didn't help me. Thanks anyway, I'll try to figure it out by myself.", "timestamp": "2026-04-27T07:27:08.323000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["183782216353054720"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1498223318862401548", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1498225443403464805", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 19, "author_id": "183782216353054720", "author_name": "omnichromia", "author_bot": false, "content": "if it didn't help, then when opening the `.csv` file, you'll need to open it from within Excel instead of from the file folder. (You may need to tell it to show you \"All Files\".) Excel should then ask you for additional instructions;\n\nChoose \"Delimited\", hit Next\nCheck \"Comma\" and uncheck all others, hit Next\nChoose \"Text\" and hit Finish", "timestamp": "2026-04-27T07:33:01.390000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["265494179222650891"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "FuHuaApprove", "emoji_id": "660878725356847105", "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1498225441339871242", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 8812, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1402941858606219294/1498225441339871242/image.png?ex=6a324dac&is=6a30fc2c&hm=019d2474aafd8a9e7e00085f207f176232c489812ff97bc303d3fd44780d7296&"}, {"id": "1498225441612365936", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 18544, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1402941858606219294/1498225441612365936/image.png?ex=6a324dac&is=6a30fc2c&hm=aedaa10a44043274b73e53aa614df6213afb23366ef741ec0cd5550fc42c8c36&"}, {"id": "1498225441989988473", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 29715, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1402941858606219294/1498225441989988473/image.png?ex=6a324dad&is=6a30fc2d&hm=dd3f94b3c9dd035c5198f9aacd5ce7f47e28bebe0546f455b3ce40004c196cb8&"}, {"id": "1498225442576924703", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 21673, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1402941858606219294/1498225442576924703/image.png?ex=6a324dad&is=6a30fc2d&hm=8f4af2f00851e365edb14487175c82aa759fcc0d3e7c0644dc11984fe83fc42f&"}, {"id": "1498225443160199339", "filename": "image.png", "content_type